cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it as below."
title: "College ROI Data: 30-year net present value of U.S. colleges and majors"
type: dataset
authors:
  - name: "LE TEEN"
    website: "https://le-teen.com"
abstract: >-
  Clean, citable tables on the lifetime financial return of U.S. colleges and
  majors: 30-year net present value by school and state, cohort-weighted ROI by
  major category, the out-of-state cost premium, and an AI-exposure score per
  major. Derived from FREOPP (2021), NCES IPEDS (2023-24 Final), BEA Regional
  Price Parities (2023), Microsoft Research "Working with AI" (2025), the
  Anthropic Economic Index (2025), and Census ACS 2022 PUMS.
keywords:
  - college ROI
  - higher education
  - student debt
  - net present value
  - college majors
  - tuition
  - IPEDS
  - FREOPP
license: CC-BY-4.0
url: "https://le-teen.com/methodology"
repository-code: "https://github.com/thomasthinks/college-roi-data"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-07-14"
doi: "10.5281/zenodo.21351602"
